"DOOM" Vol.36 : Black Metal Terrorist

Black Metal Terrorist - Deterrence. Afraid. Then join. Media covers. Then right and wrong become just. According to them. Coming from the east are called rioters. But in the west, trampling on your own parents. The formula for assembling, so that religion becomes territory. black metal. I heard music on the street while others were praying. Others prayed, my friend sacrificed his life. Then the others blamed my parents. when my neighbor gave birth to his youngest child. Right. Trembling. Black Metal Terrorist.
